des:
This Alexa Skill is a Voice Avatar of Victoria lynn Weston, Founder and CEO of Studio Carlton. Ask Victoria questions like; 

+ What does Studio Carlton do? 
+ Are you a business intuitive consultant? 
+ What is intuition? 
+ Is everyone intuitive? What are your hobbies? 
+ Do you like to cook? 
+ What do you do for a living? 
+ Tell me a Fun Fact about you. 

You will hear Victoria give you answer in her own recorded voice.

Follow Victoria on LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/in/mediaquire/

Would you like your own Voice Avatar? Visit: https://www.StudioCarlton.com/Voice-Avatar
